{"tid":1758774,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"傳真社:觀塘安利選區點票時，發現一張來自港島區已蓋印選票","createTime":"2019-11-27T09:20:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-27T14:00:11.000Z","uid":110259,"like":39,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"f80800374cab29331c9d0610cc52814958a72305","tid":1758774,"uid":110259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T09:20:26.000Z","msg":"【區選】觀塘安利選區迦密梁省德學校票站(J1001)點票時，發現一張來自東區翡翠選區(C14)的已蓋印選票。<br />\n安利選區兩名參選人引述票站主任解釋是「印刷錯誤」，不過票站主任同時透露，撇除該「港島票」，選票存根數目與收回的選票數目相符。傳真社就此向選舉事務處查詢，至截稿時未有回覆。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/factwire/photos/a.437287353144991/1274320372775014/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ffactwire%2Fphotos%2Fa.437287353144991%2F1274320372775014%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=CdC2hxDFSK2eX8E0jz8mRKDCEJE6krTJKQ6%2BfiBCJRk%3D&h=7eb7e682\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/factwire/photos/a.437287353144991/1274320372775014/?type=3&amp;theater</a>"},{"pid":"9a82efd718c010c4d2e4831200fe9a376423a998","tid":1758774,"uid":68689,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T09:22:15.000Z","msg":"港島區選票都得 咁condom都得啦"},{"pid":"b4701277a1ce42e8b3dce4effcf5240a6487e874","tid":1758774,"uid":60200,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T09:24:31.000Z","msg":"得一張印錯?"},{"pid":"0ccb2b6e4a940a230044023644080fa1e7805b16","tid":1758774,"uid":224869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T09:24:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bffa0bdd8dcd91c5008bb949e6116b9a86b635bd","tid":1758774,"uid":32934,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T09:24:54.000Z","msg":"1. 當日有冇監獄票<br />\n2. 有既話混入之前有冇望望"},{"pid":"ffcd3432ff7ddf725bb60da7fb3187c78ba776f8","tid":1758774,"uid":331421,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T09:26:01.000Z","msg":"主任：屌，印左果啲係畀廢老隊果啲嫁<img src=\"/assets/fa